---
title: Peking-Style Tofu & Ginger-Soy Veggies with Garlic Rice & Roasted Peanuts
description: Behind every great stir-fry, there's got to be a great sauce! This one has sweet chilli, fresh ginger, garlic and soy sauce, and it's a knockout. Toss it through tofu and a medley of veggies for a fast and easy weeknight winner.
